# Assets Directory

Place your images and other static assets here.

Images placed in this directory will be:
- Automatically optimized at build time
- Converted to modern formats (WebP/AVIF)
- Properly sized and compressed
- Given proper cache headers

Example structure:
```
src/assets/
├── projects/
│   ├── project-1-hero.jpg
│   └── project-1-screenshot.png
├── profile.jpg
└── og-image.jpg
```

## Usage in Components

```astro
---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImage from '@/assets/projects/project-1-hero.jpg';
---

<Image 
  src={heroImage} 
  alt="Project hero image" 
  width={1200}
  height={630}
  format="webp"
  quality={80}
/>
```

## Usage in MDX Content

```mdx
---
title: My Project
heroImage: ../../assets/projects/project-1-hero.jpg
---

import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImage from '../../assets/projects/project-1-hero.jpg';

<Image src={heroImage} alt="Hero" width={800} height={600} />
```
